Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.51,0:16:36.81,IN-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我會把你的心 帶到新的高度
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.41,IN-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}壓倒一切的魅力
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.55,IN-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}已然震撼全場 必須的吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.18,IN-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我來讓你心跳加速
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.00,IN-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}來吧！好戲開場！
