Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.15,IN-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.22,IN-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}這景色 只有我一人知曉！
